{
  "stem": "18778.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Meanwhile, getting back to the-- the espionage agent once more, when we arrived in Cuba, he demanded to be allowed to go on land.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the captain thought that he would pressure him and say, if our passengers can't get off, you can't get off.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And so we have gestapo on board, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Wherever there was German, there was gestapo.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They posed as firemen among the crew, but they were gestapo.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And the gestapo said to the captain, if you don't let him off, we have your family in Germany.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so they threatened him, and he had to let the spy go on land, and he did his business there with the agents and-- and that was that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Mission accomplished.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And meanwhile, we were the pawns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the book that was written, through the efforts--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had no idea about that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I guess the captain felt it best not to say anything to the committee about that either.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only when the facts came out when the book was written did we find that out.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "After loading provisions the day after the ship left Havana, and while we were still in the harbor, one afternoon after lunch a gentleman who had been very despondent jumped overboard.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "A sailor jumped after him, and he cut his-- the man cut his wrists.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the sailor did save him, and the man was taken to a hospital in Havana, but his wife and daughter were not allowed to join him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They went back with the ship, and eventually, when he-- his physical wounds were healed, the Cubans sent him back to England to join his family.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it was in full view of the passengers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think my mother kind of whisked me away.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
